r reliability and bottlenecks in domestic engine development."},{"citations":{"a834da70-5664-4631-bba7-dba8ef82cd52_942464069":100.0},"text":"The J-10B, an improved version of the J-10A, was successfully tested in December 2008 and featured a redesigned intake channel."},{"citations":{"a834da70-5664-4631-bba7-dba8ef82cd52_942464069":100.0},"text":"The J-10C, introduced in 2017, includes further advancements such as an active phased array radar, enhancing its combat capabilities."},{"citations":{"7662ae65-98c5-4a3f-9b24-83a5f9fb7a72_115461755":100.0},"text":"The J-10C offers multiple features and performance advantages over the F-16, particularly in terms of armament, flight, and overall performance."}],"answer":[{"citations":{"7662ae65-98c5-4a3f-9b24-83a5f9fb7a72_115461755":100.0},"text":"The Chinese J-10C fighter jet has been sold to Pakistan, marking a significant milestone in its export journey."},{"citations":{"cd6f7c06-5e22-4103-9de2-9817a9a60efa_121885815":100.0},"text":"Pakistan began receiving deliveries of the J-10C in February 2022, with the aircraft being formally inducted into the Pakistan Air Force (PAF) during a ceremony at Kamra Airbase."},{"citations":{"a834da70-5664-4631-bba7-dba8ef82cd52_942464069":100.0},"text":"The Pakistan Air Force has ordered a total of 36 J-10CE fighters, which is the export version of the J-10C, to enhance its air defense capabilities."},{"citations":{"cd6f7c06-5e22-4103-9de2-9817a9a60efa_121885815":100.0},"text":"China is expected to deliver 25 of these J-10C fighter jets to Pakistan, significantly bolstering the country's combat readiness."},{"citations":{"7662ae65-98c5-4a3f-9b24-83a5f9fb7a72_1044319203":100.0},"text":"The J-10C is considered a strong alternative to the U.S. fourth-generation F-16 fighter jet, which has led some countries to consider acquiring it."},{"citations":{"7662ae65-98c5-4a3f-9b24-83a5f9fb7a72_1044319203":100.0},"text":"Turkey has shown interest in the J-10C as a potential replacement for the U.S. F