 inspiration for others seeking to enter the construction industry."},{"citations":{"c40b5c1c-6e7a-45f6-a314-adcf276acb8c_663217418":100.0},"text":"The government can support women in construction by investing in educational programs, vocational training, mentorship opportunities, and inclusive policies promoting gender equality and non-discrimination."},{"citations":{"c40b5c1c-6e7a-45f6-a314-adcf276acb8c_663217418":100.0},"text":"Empowering women in the construction industry contributes to gender equality and sustainable development, benefiting society as a whole."},{"citations":{"589ca671-5a89-4831-abc9-9f0a59aeb2b9_935642743":100.0},"text":"States and local administrations are increasingly prioritizing diversity in companies when awarding contracts, creating more opportunities for women in construction."},{"citations":{"589ca671-5a89-4831-abc9-9f0a59aeb2b9_935642743":100.0},"text":"Ferridiana Cerato emphasized the importance of representation and mentorship for women in construction, noting that seeing another Latina in the field inspired her career path."},{"citations":{"08bf5561-f112-47d8-ae82-2041a9b4fc15_17345750":100.0},"text":"Noura Jamal Taha Mohamed, a 36-year-old woman from Assiut, became the first woman in Upper Egypt to obtain a heavy equipment driver's license, overcoming societal bullying and traditional gender restrictions."},{"citations":{"08bf5561-f112-47d8-ae82-2041a9b4fc15_17345750":100.0},"text":"Noura learned to drive a loader to improve her income and help her husband pay for the treatment of their two children with autism."},{"citations":{"08bf5561-f112-47d8-ae82-2041a9b4fc15_17345750":100.0},"text":"Despite initial surprise and skepticism from the training center, Noura received support and successfully completed her training in heavy equipment operation."},{"citations":{"08bf5561-f112-47d8-ae82-2041a9b4fc15_17345750":100.0},"text":"Noura's determination and love for the profession helped her excel during the training period, showing proficiency and overcoming initial challenges."},{"citations":{"08bf5561-f112-47d8-ae82-2041a9b4fc15_17345750":100.0},"text":"Noura plans to seek employment with a company that values women's work and aims to develop her life for the better."},{"citations":{"fa814205-0346-442b-87c5-93059583ffff_953125432":100.0},"text":"Li Rui, a female tower crane operator, works at a construction site in Xiongan New District and has successfully saved over 70,000 yuan in less than a year."},{"citations":{"fa814205-0346-442b-87c5-93059583ffff_953125432":100.0},"text":"Li Rui's job as a tower crane driver involves operating heavy machinery with precision, requiring excellent psychological quality and superb operation skills."},{"citations":{"fa814205-0346-442b-87c5-93059583ffff_953125432":100.0},"text":"Li Rui earns a monthly income of over 9,000 yuan and appreciates the timely payment system for migrant workers at the construction site."},{"citations":{"fa814205-0346-442b-87c5-93059583ffff_953125432":100.0},"text":"Li Rui highlights improved living conditions at the construction site, including air-conditioned dormitories, 24-hour hot water, and affordable, delicious food."},{"citations":{"fa814205-0346-442b-87c5-93059583ffff_953125432":100.0},"text":"Li Rui invests in her career by purchasing learning materials and applying for professional certificates, such as an excavator certificate, to expand her skills."},{"citations":{"fa814205-0346-442b-87c5-93059583ffff_953125432":100.0},"text":"Li Rui expresses pride in witnessing the growth of Xiongan New Area and contributing to its development through her work as a crane operator."},{"citations":{"589ca671-5a89-4831-abc9-9f0a59aeb2b9_935642743":100.0},"text":"The share of women among construction workers in the United States reached its highest level at 14.1 percent last month."},{"citations":{"589ca671-5a89-4831-abc9-9f0a59aeb2b9_935642743":100.0},"text":"The construction sector is experiencing a labor shortage, partly due to the retiremen