trategy, which includes signing the Women\u2019s Empowerment Principles and offering male parental leave, has significantly increased female representation in leadership and technical positions."},{"citations":{"65fbc85d-e429-4d5a-9efc-ced8faf79161_540514178":100.0},"text":"Companies like Meest Group have adjusted operational processes and introduced technology to create more comfortable working conditions for women in traditionally male roles."},{"citations":{"59271291-9f4e-455a-b133-f91be9278e03_342512573":100.0},"text":"Embedding inclusion efforts at all organizational levels ensures gender parity becomes the norm, fostering a welcoming environment for women in construction."},{"citations":{"c40b5c1c-6e7a-45f6-a314-adcf276acb8c_663217418":100.0},"text":"By addressing gender biases and implementing fair practices, organizations can attract and retain talented women, contributing to sustainable development and industry growth."}],"answer":[{"citations":{"c40b5c1c-6e7a-45f6-a314-adcf276acb8c_663217418":100.0},"text":"Women are increasingly entering crane operation roles, challenging the historical perception of construction as a male-dominated industry."},{"citations":{"c40b5c1c-6e7a-45f6-a314-adcf276acb8c_663217418":100.0},"text":"This shift is driven by the dismantling of societal norms and gender stereotypes that have traditionally excluded women from technical roles."},{"citations":{"485cdc95-bbf9-4578-9b0d-47d964d3e7aa_207874500":100.0},"text":"Profiles like Farkhana Safargaleeva, who has worked as a crane operator for over 15 years, and Natalia Danilova, a compressor operator with 16 years of experience, highlight women\u2019s passion and commitment to these roles."},{"citations":{"485cdc95-bbf9-4578-9b0d-47d964d3e7aa_207874500":100.0},"text":"Women in crane operation excel due to qualities such as calmness and attentiveness, which are critical for the precision and safety required in these roles."},{"citations":{"485cdc95-bbf9-4578-9b0d-47d964d3e7aa_207874500