{"is_ragtime":true,"metadata":{"team_id":"T215","run_id":"gar","topic_id":"1057","request_id":"1057","narrative_id":"1057"},"responses":[{"citations":{"a89e20ea-c2ae-4600-8704-7d23939dacc1_458215749":100.0},"text":"Vertical gardens, also known as green walls, are increasingly recognized for their ability to enhance indoor environments through both aesthetic and functional benefits."},{"citations":{"a89e20ea-c2ae-4600-8704-7d23939dacc1_458215749":100.0},"text":"One of the most significant advantages of green walls is their capacity to improve air quality by reducing harmful pollutants such as nitrogen dioxide (NO2) and particulate matter (PM10) by approximately 40% and 60%, respectively."},{"citations":{"a89e20ea-c2ae-4600-8704-7d23939dacc1_458215749":100.0},"text":"In specific settings like classrooms, green walls have been shown to lower fine particulate matter (PM2.5) by about 10% and ozone (O3) concentrations by 30%, contributing to healthier indoor air."},{"citations":{"a89e20ea-c2ae-4600-8704-7d23939dacc1_458215749":100.0},"text":"Unlike traditional air purification systems, green walls operate naturally and energy-efficiently, relying on self-circulation without the need for electricity."},{"citations":{"a89e20ea-c2ae-4600-8704-7d23939dacc1_458215749":100.0},"text":"Beyond air purification, vertical gardens play a role in temperature regulation, helping to conserve energy and reduce carbon emissions within indoor spaces."},{"citations":{"a89e20ea-c2ae-4600-8704-7d23939dacc1_458215749":100.0},"text":"This temperature regulation can lead to lower heating and cooling costs, making green walls a sustainable choice for homeowners seeking energy efficiency."},{"citations":{"a89e20ea-c2ae-4600-8704-7d23939dacc1_458215749":100.0},"text":"In addition to environmental benefits, green walls can positively impact mental health by creating a calming and visually appealing atmosphere that promotes relaxation and well-being."},{"citations":{"a89e20ea-c2ae-4600-8704-7d23939dacc1_458215749":100.0},"text":"For homeowners concerned about maintenance, there are several plant options suitable for green walls that require minimal upkeep, such as Dragon Tubeh, Junzi Bamboo, Wu Bamboo, Turtle Vine, Cannonflower, and Honeysuckle."},{"citations":{"a89e20ea-c2ae-4600-8704-7d23939dacc1_458215749":100.0},"text":"These low-maintenance plants are adaptable to various indoor climates, making them ideal for vertical gardens in diverse home settings."},{"citations":{"a89e20ea-c2ae-4600-8704-7d23939dacc1_458215749":100.0},"text":"By combining aesthetic appeal with practical benefits like air purification, temperature regulation, and mental health improvements, vertical gardens offer a compelling solution for homeowners seeking to create a healthier and more sustainable living space."}],"answer":[{"citations":{"a89e20ea-c2ae-4600-8704-7d23939dacc1_458215749":100.0},"text":"Vertical gardens, also known as green walls, are increasingly recognized for their ability to enhance indoor environments through both aesthetic and functional benefits."},{"citations":{"a89e20ea-c2ae-4600-8704-7d23939dacc1_458215749":100.0},"text":"One of the most significant advantages of green walls is their capacity to improve air quality by reducing harmful pollutants such as nitrogen dioxide (NO2) and particulate matter (PM10) by approximately 40% and 60%, respectively."},{"citations":{"a89e20ea-c2ae-4600-8704-7d23939dacc1_458215749":100.0},"text":"In specific settings like classrooms, green walls have been shown to lower fine particulate matter (PM2.5) by about 10% and ozone (O3) concentrations by 30%, contributing to healthier indoor air."},{"citations":{"a89e20ea-c2ae-4600-8704-7d23939dacc1_458215749":100.0},"text":"Unlike traditional air purification systems, green walls operate naturally and energy-efficiently, relying on self-circulation without the need for electricity."},{"citations":{"a89e20ea-c2ae-4600-8704-7d23939dacc1_458215749":100.0},"text":"Beyond air purification, vertical gardens play a role in temperature regulation, helping to conserve energy and reduce carbon emissions within indoor spaces."},{"citations":{"a89e20ea-c2ae-4600-8704-7d23939dacc1_458215749":100.0},"text":"This temperature regulation can lead to lower heating and cooling costs, making green walls a sustainable choice for homeowners seeking energy efficiency."},{"citations":{"a89e20ea-c2ae-4600-8704-7d23939dacc1_458215749":100.0},"text":"In addition to environmental benefits, green walls can positively impact mental health by creating a calming and visually appealing atmosphere that promotes relaxation and well-being."},{"citations":{"a89e20ea-c2ae-4600-8704-7d23939dacc1_458215749":100.0},"text":"For homeowners concerned about maintenance, there are several plant options suitable for green walls that require minimal upkeep, such as Dragon Tubeh, Junzi Bamboo, Wu Bamboo, Turtle Vine, Cannonflower, and Honeysuckle."},{"citations":{"a89e20ea-c2ae-4600-8704-7d23939dacc1_458215749":100.0},"text":"These low-maintenance plants are adaptable to various indoor climates, making them ideal for vertical gardens in diverse home settings."},{"citations":{"a89e20ea-c2ae-4600-8704-7d23939dacc1_458215749":100.0},"text":"By combining aesthetic appeal with practical benefits like air purification, temperature regulation, and mental health improvements, vertical gardens offer a compelling solution for homeowners seeking to create a healthier and more sustainable living space."}],"references":["a89e20ea-c2ae-4600-8704-7d23939dacc1_458215749"],"documents":{"a89e20ea-c2ae-4600-8704-7d23939dacc1_458215749":{"id":"a89e20ea-c2ae-4600-8704-7d23939dacc1_458215749","text":"In order to improve the environmental air quality and let children learn with peace of mind, the Taichung Municipal Environmental Protection Bureau has continued to build a clean air green wall in the school. This year, 12 schools in Jianping Elementary School, Juren Elementary School and Chongde Elementary School have received subsidies from the Environmental Protection Department.\nAccording to the Environmental Protection Bureau, through the installation of clean air green walls, indoor air quality can be improved. At present, space such as classroom corridors and flower stands outside the daughter wall in Taichung City can be planted, which can achieve the benefits of dust retention, air pollution absorption and temperature regulation.\nIn order to strengthen the protection of the school environment for children, the Taichung City Environmental Protection Bureau expanded the subsidy for the construction of a clean air green wall on the campus, and the current subsidy amount to 1.76 million yuan, with an area of 358 square meters.\nThe Environmental Protection Bureau stressed that currently selected plants that can purify the air and do not need to spend too much money and time to maintain include the Dragon Tubeh, the Junzi and Wu Bamboo, the Turtle, the Cannonflower or the Honeysuckle.\nHow good is the effect of clean air green wall?\nAccording to international research, vertical clean air green walls can reduce the concentration of nitrogen dioxide (NO2) and particulate matter (PM10) by about 40% and 60%. In addition, green walls can also reduce the concentration of fine particulate matter (PM2.5) in classrooms by about 10% and the concentration of ozone (O3) by about 30%.\nGreen wall is the most natural and energy efficient air purification facilities, no need to plug in electricity, self-circulation, to achieve the purpose of air purification, can be called the \"most environmentally friendly air purifier\".\nChen Hongyi, director of the Environmental Protection Bureau, said that in addition to blocking outdoor pollutants and improving indoor air, the air green wall can also adjust the temperature and drive energy conservation and carbon reduction. Next year, Taichung City is expected to expand the subsidy target, including community activity centers, public kindergartens and environmental night markets.\n# Green Wall # Air # Cleanliness # Campus # Environment","metadata":{"content_type":"text/html","provenance":"cc-news_2021-0034.json.gz:14270","uncompressed_offset":458215749,"url":"www.chinatimes.com/realtimenews/20211125003391-260405","warc_date":"2021-11-25T05:58:05.000Z","warc_filename":"<urn:uuid:a89e20ea-c2ae-4600-8704-7d23939dacc1>","warc_url":"https://www.chinatimes.com/realtimenews/20211125003391-260405"},"created":"2021-11-25T06:35:23.000Z","lang":"eng"}}}
