ortuguese, and Spanish."},{"citations":{"79ebd9ed-d25a-485c-b9d2-54a988b77025_299669427":100.0},"text":"The tool has demonstrated its ability to replicate accents accurately, as shown in experiments with voices like Donald Trump and David Attenborough speaking in multiple languages."},{"citations":{"3fe50e8c-745c-497f-9ba9-0f03c0f990cd_628094452":100.0},"text":"China Media Group has launched its first AI-dubbed English documentary, showcasing advancements in AI technology for global media outreach."},{"citations":{"3fe50e8c-745c-497f-9ba9-0f03c0f990cd_628094452":100.0},"text":"The AI-dubbed documentary was originally produced in Mandarin and made accessible to English-speaking audiences, enhancing global reach and impact."},{"citations":{"3fe50e8c-745c-497f-9ba9-0f03c0f990cd_628094452":100.0},"text":"AI voice cloning technology was used to create lifelike digital replicas of human voices, maintaining the authenticity of the original narration while making it understandable in English."},{"citations":{"3fe50e8c-745c-497f-9ba9-0f03c0f990cd_628094452":100.0},"text":"The use of AI in dubbing ensures the delivery of content with emotional depth and cultural nuances intact, improving accessibility for diverse audiences."},{"citations":{"9dacbd3f-013e-444d-8a47-ee5706dbe14d_512424110":100.0},"text":"Amazon Alexa demonstrated a feature where it mimics the voice of a deceased relative using less than a minute of recorded content."},{"citations":{"9dacbd3f-013e-444d-8a47-ee5706dbe14d_512424110":100.0},"text":"The new voice imitation function is based on advances in text-to-speech technology, allowing high-quality replication with minimal data."},{"citations":{"9dacbd3f-013e-444d-8a47-ee5706dbe14d_512424110":100.0},"text":"Amazon's Chief Scientist Rohit Prasad stated that the technology aims to deepen the 'humanity' of AI voice assistants by enabling lasting personal relationships with deceased relatives."},{"citations":{"cd68dcb4-80b0-47ef-9937-5e2e4cf6af2e_771817032":100.0},