47ca-aaad-05e0fb187180_520597399":100.0},"text":"Goodall advises against confrontational approaches, emphasizing collaboration and understanding to achieve conservation goals."},{"citations":{"1fa58c5e-416a-418f-8de6-22f4a81873e8_687307734":100.0},"text":"Dr. Jane Goodall emphasizes that humans are not separate from the natural world but are deeply dependent on healthy ecosystems for food, water, and overall well-being."},{"citations":{"1fa58c5e-416a-418f-8de6-22f4a81873e8_687307734":100.0},"text":"She advocates for balancing environmental conservation with maintaining economic stability, as making people poorer while saving plants and animals is not a viable solution."},{"citations":{"95f67cee-331c-42fd-9d52-cb7bad432c19_898632871":100.0},"text":"Jane Goodall believes that small actions taken by millions or billions of individuals can collectively change the world."},{"citations":{"95f67cee-331c-42fd-9d52-cb7bad432c19_898632871":100.0},"text":"She stresses that individuals make an impact on the environment every day and must choose what kind of impact they want to make."},{"citations":{"4ba15d10-6c38-48a0-8bc6-a4acdc286647_602215183":100.0},"text":"The Apple TV+ series 'Jane,' inspired by Goodall's teachings, aims to encourage children to take a stand for endangered species and environmental conservation."},{"citations":{"4ba15d10-6c38-48a0-8bc6-a4acdc286647_602215183":100.0},"text":"The 'Jane' series features a young protagonist inspired by Goodall, focusing on endangered species and blending live action with CGI to engage viewers."},{"citations":{"4ba15d10-6c38-48a0-8bc6-a4acdc286647_602215183":100.0},"text":"Each episode of 'Jane' ends with video chats featuring real-life animal experts, highlighting diverse voices including women and people of color."},{"citations":{"4c0ee3ad-3947-4c32-9bdc-e1ea45fa3dd9_55984504":100.0},"text":"The Jane Goodall Sustainability Academy in Taiwan will be the first experimental primary school in Asia focusing on conservation and su